## ⚙️ TECH STACK (Fixed)

| Layer | Technology |
|---|---|
| Framework | **Next.js** (TypeScript) App Router — OR — **React** (JavaScript) Vite |
| Styling | **Tailwind CSS** (`darkMode: 'class'`) |
| Backend | **Supabase** via `@supabase/ssr` |
| Deployment | **Netlify** |

---

## 📁 KEY FILES — WHAT LIVES WHERE

| File | Purpose | Breaks When |
|---|---|---|
| `middleware.ts` | Root level — calls `updateSession()` | Missing or in `/app` → auth fails after token expiry |
| `lib/supabase/client.ts` | Browser Supabase — `'use client'` ONLY | Used in Server Component → cookie errors |
| `lib/supabase/server.ts` | Server Supabase — Server Components, Route Handlers | `getSession()` used → insecure auth |
| `lib/supabase/middleware.ts` | `updateSession()` function | Not called in middleware → sessions stale |
| `app/auth/callback/route.ts` | OAuth + magic link exchange | Missing → all OAuth fails |
| `app/api/webhooks/stripe/route.ts` | Stripe events | `request.json()` used → signature fails |
| `supabase/migrations/` | SQL migration files | Not pushed → tables don't exist |
| `.env.local` | Local env vars | Not copied to Netlify → prod broken |

