## 🌍 ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES

```bash
# .env.local                                    Netlify (add manually — not auto-synced)
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL              →         add
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY         →         add
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY             →         add  (server only)
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY                     →         use sk_live_ in prod
NEXT_PUBLIC_STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY    →         use pk_live_ in prod
STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET                 →         unique per endpoint AND env
STRIPE_PRICE_ID                       →         RECREATE in live mode
NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL                  →         https://your-app.netlify.app
RESEND_API_KEY                        →         add (if email enabled)
```

