## 📊 SUPABASE CHECKLIST

```
□ Project active? (free tier pauses after 7 days — restore at supabase.com)
□ Migrations pushed? (supabase/migrations/ SQL applied to Supabase)
□ Profile trigger exists?
  SELECT * FROM pg_trigger WHERE tgname = 'on_auth_user_created';
□ RLS policies on all tables?
  SELECT * FROM pg_policies WHERE tablename = 'your_table';
□ Redirect URLs: localhost + Netlify prod URL + custom domain?
□ Social OAuth: only works on live URL — NEVER on localhost
□ Env vars in both .env.local AND Netlify dashboard?
```

