## 💳 STRIPE GO-LIVE CHECKLIST

```
□ Recreate ALL products/prices in LIVE mode (don't transfer from test)
□ STRIPE_SECRET_KEY → sk_live_...
□ NEXT_PUBLIC_STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY → pk_live_...
□ Create new webhook endpoint with production URL
□ STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET → live endpoint's secret (different from test!)
□ STRIPE_PRICE_ID → live mode price ID
□ Update ALL 4 Stripe vars in Netlify environment variables
□ Trigger fresh Netlify deploy after env var changes
```

