## ⚠️ CRITICAL RULES — REPEATED AT BOTTOM (HIGH ATTENTION ZONE)

1. **`getUser()` not `getSession()`** — always in server-side code
2. **`request.text()` not `request.json()`** — always in Stripe webhook handlers
3. **`lib/supabase/server.ts`** in Server Components — **`lib/supabase/client.ts`** in `'use client'` only
4. **`middleware.ts` at project root** — never inside `/app`
5. **`await cookies()`** — required in Next.js 15
6. **Never `NEXT_PUBLIC_`** on service role key
7. **Never `@supabase/auth-helpers-nextjs`** — use `@supabase/ssr`
8. **Social OAuth never works on localhost** — test on deployed URL only
9. **`.env.local` is NOT auto-synced** to Netlify — add vars manually
10. **Stripe test/live are fully isolated** — recreate everything in live mode
11. **`/audit-codebase` first** on every new project — never skip
12. **`cursor-composer` for agent tasks** — not Sonnet, not Opus
13. **Identify project type** before auditing — SaaS/e-commerce/AI/booking all have different failure modes
14. **Run `/check-mcp`** if MCP tools don't appear — they fail silently
15. **Env file is `.env`** in Rocket projects — not `.env.local` — both work, don't rename
16. **MCP credentials in mcp.json** — paste directly per project, they don't auto-read from `.env`
17. **`memory-bank/instincts/`** — read at session start, write via `/reflect` or `/learn-eval`
